title: Starts of the Week + Week 5 Breakdown, Trapper Keepers - Fantasy Football Podcast for 10/7
description:
Week 5 is here and The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike, and Jason dive into Week 5 matchups and reveal their Starts of the Week! Plus, injury updates, and a new edition of “Never Not Working!” Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for October 7th, 2021.
  
 (05:45) - Never Not Working
 (11:55) - NFL News 
 (23:00) - Fantasy Forecast
 (23:40) - Jets vs Falcons (London)
 (29:55) - Packers at Bengals
 (33:05) - Lions at Vikings
 (37:15) - Broncos at Steelers
 (42:55) - Dolphins at Buccaneers 
 (47:00) - Saints at Washington Football Team
 (52:15) - Titans at Jaguars
 (56:30) - Starts of the Week
 (56:50) - RB Starts of the Week
 (59:30) - QB Starts of the Week
 (01:02:25) - WR Starts of the Week
 (01:04:50) - TE Starts of the Week
 (01:07:50) - Boom Boom Kicker of the Week
